CompanyDescription.value: MindWalk (NASDAQ: HYFT) is a Bio-Native AI company pioneering the integration of artificial intelligence, multi-omics data, and advanced laboratory research to accelerate the discovery and development of biologics. Through its proprietary LensAI platform and HYFT technology, MindWalk partners with global pharmaceutical and biotechnology companies to drive innovation, de-risk drug development, and unlock new therapeutic possibilities.
